author: Saikat Das
title: Covid fallout: Rate transmission far cry despite liquidity overhang
description: The banking system has hit the surplus level seen during the demonetisation period.
content:
Mumbai: Surplus cash in the banking system has surged to as much as Rs 4.74 lakh crore, surpassing liquidity levels seen four years ago during the demonetisation period.
